NAME
    marc-record-stats - Tool to work with MARC::Record::Stats on MARC
    dataset.

SYNOPSIS
     marc-record-stats [-h] [-i format] [--version] marc_file

DESCRIPTION
    It supports MARC XML files now.

ARGUMENTS
    *       "-h"

            Print help.

    *       "-i format"

            Input MARC format.

            Possible formats are:

            *   xml

    *       "--version"

            Print version of script.

    *       "marc_file"

            MARC file name for statistics.

REPOSITORY
    <https://github.com/michal-josef-spacek/App-MARC-Record-Stats>

